Core product rule:\
This is a warehouse floor app, not a management dashboard and not a full ERP.\
\
The phone app should help an operator answer:\
- What am I working on?\
- What needs scanned?\
- What load/task/shipment am I attached to?\
- Where does this material go?\
- What needs review?\
