Scanner behavior:\
- Today: shortcut only, no scanner lock\
- Receiving Load screen: scanner locked to loadId\
- Inventory: scanner performs global inventory lookup\
- Putaway Task screen: scanner locked to taskId\
- Shipping Load screen: scanner locked to shipmentId\
