RECEIVING TAB\
\
Receiving is the strongest workflow in the app.\
\
Receiving main screen groups:\
1. Ready to Receive\
2. In Progress\
3. Needs Review\
\
Receiving load cards should show:\
- Shipment ID\
- Carrier\
- Vendor\
- Dock door\
- Status\
- Time arrived / staged\
- Exception badge if needed\
\
Example:\
Shipment T-4471\
Old Dominion \'b7 Door 7\
Vendor: Midwest Parts\
22 pallets \'b7 Staged\
