2. Scan staged product\
3. Confirm loaded items\
4. Mark missing / damaged\
5. Complete shipment\
6. Generate shipper PO / paperwork\
\
Exception types:\
- Overage\
- Shortage\
- Damage\
- Missing paperwork\
- Unknown SKU\
- Quantity mismatch\
- QC hold\
- Wrong item\
\
Design requirements:\
- Keep the existing premium iOS visual direction.\
- Use rounded cards, clean spacing, soft shadows, navy/blue SkyView feel.\
- Large tap targets.\
- No cluttered ERP tables.\
- Mobile-first.\
- Make every screen feel like a working warehouse floor tool.\
- Prioritize screen hierarchy, scanner state, and workflow clarity over decorative polish.\
\
